---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
import StaffList from "../components/Sections/StaffList.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Acerca de mí - Alicia López"
  description="Learn about our church's history, mission, values, and the people who make our community special."
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="Alicia López" 
    subtitle="Mi historia, recorrido y valores"
    backgroundImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438032005730-c779502df39b?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center"
  />
  
  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Mi visión</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            Soy Psicologa, Especialista en Terapia Familiar y de Pareja con enfoque Sistémico, y
            formacion como Tanatologa. Cuento con una Maestría en Terapia Existencial y
            Fenomenologica, formacion que ha enriquecido profundamente mi manera de acompanar a
            las personas en sus procesos emocionales y existenciales.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Mi historia</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            A lo largo de más de 20 años he colaborado en el ambito educativo desde el departamento
            psicopedagogico de diversas instituciones educativas, brindando orientacion, contencion y
            guía tanto a estudiantes como a docentes y familias.

            Ademas he participatdo como coautora en varios libros enfocados en Orientacion Educativa
            y Tutoria, aportando herramientas prácticas para el acompanamiento integral de ninas,
            niños y adolescentes.

            Mi compromiso es ofrecer un espacio terapeutico seguro, empaticoy respetuoso, en donde
            cada persona pueda explorar y comprender su experiencia de vida desde una mirada
            profunda y humana.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493225457124-a3eb161ffa5f?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" 
            alt="Worship at our church" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our Core Values</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These principles guide everything we do as a church community
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Biblical Teaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We are committed to teaching God's Word faithfully and helping people apply it to their lives. We believe the Bible is God's inspired, inerrant Word and our ultimate authority.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-secondary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Authentic Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe spiritual growth happens best in community. We foster genuine relationships where people can be known, loved, and challenged to grow in their faith.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-accent-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Missional Living</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe every follower of Jesus is called to share His love with others. We equip and encourage our members to live on mission in their neighborhoods, workplaces, and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Spiritual Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We are committed to helping people grow in their relationship with Christ, becoming more like Him in their thoughts, words, and actions through discipleship and spiritual practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Spirit-Led Worship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We value authentic, heartfelt worship that glorifies God and transforms lives. We seek to create environments where people can encounter God's presence.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Servant Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We believe leadership is about service, not status. We develop and empower leaders who model Christ-like humility and sacrifice as they guide others.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Church History -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Mi recorrido</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          La historia de como llegue aquí
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
            <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1993</time>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Licenciatura en Psicología.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Universidad Nacional Autónoma de México.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1997</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Diplomado en Psicología Forense.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Universidad Nacional
                  Autónoma de México, FES. Zaragoza y Procuraduría General de Justicia
                  del Distrito Federal.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2001-2004</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Especialidad en Psicoterapia Familiar y de Pareja.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Instituto de Entrenamiento e Investigación en Psicoterapia “Personas.”
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2006-2007</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Diplomado en Problemas de Aprendizaje.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Aprendizaje. Universidad Panamericana.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2009- 2010</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Máster en Educación en la Especialidad de Asesoramiento Educativo Familiar.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Centro Universitario Villanueva, Adscrito a la Universidad Computense de Madrid.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
              <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">2019- 2020.</time>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Diplomado en Tanatología.</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Instituto Mexicano de Tanatología.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>